WEBVTT

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:04.600
Shiny's implementation in Python makes it easy to customize the look and feel of your

00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:06.040
data science app.

00:00:06.040 --> 00:00:09.920
With a single line of code, you can select between any BootSwatch themes.

00:00:09.920 --> 00:00:12.600
This is possible thanks to the new ShinySwatch package.

00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:16.760
Adapt your tool to different use cases, user preferences, or branding requirements.

00:00:16.760 --> 00:00:21.400
Learn more at shiny.positive.co.uk and let's have a quick look at some of your BootSwatch

00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:24.600
themes options.

